Name: TocLoincTermsAnsweredByLL5571
Title: Transitions of Care LOINC Terms Answered by LL5571-6 Answer List Value Set
Descriptino: This value set includes those LOINC terms that are defined to be answered by LOINC answer list LL5571-6.    Ideally, this could be intensionally defined as terms where the answer-list property is "LL5571-6", however at publication time, this property is not supported by the FHIR terminology server at tx.fhir.org.
